became the 115th person executed in the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> and the fifth in <LOCATION> Alabama </LOCATION> since the <ORGANIZATION> Supreme </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Court </ORGANIZATION> allowed states to reinstate capital punishment in 1976.
