<HEAD>Health Experts Say Swimming in Algae Is Safe</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: UPDATES with later statement advising against swimming in algae.
EDITS to trim. No pickup.</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ROME (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
