ars before he died, showed the two musicians' virtuosity most excitingly, we most enjoyed the andante movements with their beautiful melodies. And in <PERSON> Perlman </PERSON> and <PERSON> Kalichstein </PERSON>, the Mostly Mozart Festival found the men to reach and calm the listener's soul in playing them.
